<TITLE>Nashua Corporation General Information</TITLE>
<META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="coated paper, labels, imaging supplies, computer products, office supplies, photofinishing, film thermal papers, pressure-sensitive labels,  specialty papers, copier ink jet, laser printer supplies, aluminum substrates, photofinishing services">
<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Nashua Corporation is a leading manufacturer and provider of coated products, office supplies and photofinishing services that is expanding its presence around the globe.  The company offers a diverse mix of high-quality products and services including facsimile and thermal papers, pressure-sensitive labels, specialty papers and tapes, copier and laser printer supplies, and mail-order photofinishing services.">
